origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinancialCrisisReports.search_reports', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisReports.search_reports', 'description': 'This function searches for detailed reports on major financial crises within a specified time frame.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisisType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial crisis, e.g., major, minor.'}, {'name': 'timeFrame', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time frame for the search, e.g., lastDecade, nextDecade.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'reports', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching reports, each with an ID, title, and summary.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisReports.get_report_details', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisReports.get_report_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific financial crisis report given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'reportId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the financial crisis report.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the report, including full text, analysis, and conclusions.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisReports.find_emerging_markets_studies', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisReports.find_emerging_markets_studies', 'description': 'This function searches for studies on the performance of emerging markets during major financial crises.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisisType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial crisis, e.g., major, minor.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'studies', 'description': 'A list of studies, each with an ID, title, and summary.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisReports.get_us_recovery_data', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisReports.get_us_recovery_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves data on the economic recovery of the United States after a specified financial crisis.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisisType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial crisis, e.g., lastCrisis, previousCrisis.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Economic recovery data, including GDP growth, employment rates, and stock market performance.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisReports.predict_future_crisis', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisReports.predict_future_crisis', 'description': 'This function retrieves predictions from authoritative institutions on the likelihood of future financial crises within a specified time frame.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'timeFrame', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time frame for the prediction, e.g., nextDecade, nextFiveYears.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'predictions', 'description': 'Predictions on future financial crises, including probabilities and potential causes.'}]}], ['FinancialCrisisReports.get_crisis_strategies', {'name': 'FinancialCrisisReports.get_crisis_strategies', 'description': 'This function retrieves strategies for dealing with potential financial crises.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'crisisType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial crisis, e.g., potential, historical.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'strategies', 'description': 'A list of strategies, each with a description and recommended actions.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `FinancialCrisisReports.search_reports` 并传入 `crisisType` 和 `timeFrame`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "FinancialCrisisReports.search_reports",
    "args": "{'crisisType': 'major', 'timeFrame': 'lastDecade'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
